➜趣读丨成功人士都是怎么拍照的？
http://www.sohu.com/a/415701043_425113	7926
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/166d2a4154234def9162130d8aa346c3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来源：公众号跳海大院（ID：meerjump）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“不要轻易相信任何一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>双手交叉在胸前的亚洲人”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是文字君朋友东山口百惠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拾微博评论之牙慧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传授给我的箴言</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200831/d248e9c254904a2b8f3dbb467ff802e7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在她看来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手交叉于胸前的姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无异于宣告一个人成功学学家</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">或传销创始人的身份</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/9b6e6c4c44a8485a922923e9e245a996.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然也有可能是真正的成功人士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她还说岑怡诺身上有她当年的影子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当她看到有人将双手交叉于胸前时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总能让她回忆起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曾经在广西北海的那个夏天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200831/50f842be19f34ef2bd7811cc5e776b66.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那时的她，通读汉化卡耐基</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从《人性的弱点》读到《人性的光辉》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将“私募界的巴菲特”视为精神偶像</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在乌云和银滩大海之间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她像一道黑色的闪电</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在高傲地飞翔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“我要成功”四个字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">便从那时写入了她的DNA</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200831/46e8c7b8a26f43098a5c9d75f3961249.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是那个燥热的夏天过去了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是她不再渴望被印成双手交叉的公式照</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在各大演讲会场供狂热的追随者瞻仰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">她只想多接广告稿挣钱补牙</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200831/933d8535fa584caa92c2078e26778de6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/5ae0e3b8055f42749d89f1a1b33112ce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“要想成为一名成功人士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第一步要先学会摆拍照姿势”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">东山口百惠说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这也是她当年在广西北海学到的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">首先将头发梳成大人模样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后穿上一身帅气西装</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皮鞋擦得锃光瓦亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">眼神目视前方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/7cc0ed89608d449b81a6bd48a3214ba8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱马仕皮带是每一个土豪的标配</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看起来很贵，彰显着金钱地位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但成功人士的气质绝对不能有土味</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以皮带应该藏于衣服之内</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/e5998d825bc94d05a841149b2c46b071.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/ 图片来源于：凤凰网时尚/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而衣着之外最重要的莫过于pose</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最经典的是双手交叉于胸前的姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嘴角微微上扬笑而不露齿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再搭配上微微侧身的肢体设计</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就完成了一张成功人士的拍照公式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/4ef788093cab47cfa5a996b0d09a7195.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就连新东方的掌门人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和新东方的总舵主</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是这一拍照姿势的忠实拥趸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无论是学英语，还是学炒菜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功都归于共同的样子：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手交叉于胸前！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200831/d6e09f2682b140a6aa1b8f1b65c61d04.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/05dba05c844e4699b665f98d844c0a61.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/871258d0bd6e4b249ecd4c99acee4556.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就像红灯和铃声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">之于巴甫洛夫的狗一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手交叉于胸前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是成功人士拍照的条件反射</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丝毫没有蹉跎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功就是如此干净利落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/0ce7031edac549a282bb5cb07135f4a6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/吴磊弟弟完美掌握成功人士拍照精髓/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而真的成功人士</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">敢于以A打头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">命名自己的微信昵称</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">5A级的昵称</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牢牢占据社交通讯录的头把交椅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手交叉于胸前的头像意味着“专业”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们在朋友圈里随时随地分享</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">价值百万的人寿、地产生意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200831/8333c29e8e6c4983aa35241801c32de9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除双手交叉于胸前的姿势之外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">东山口百惠还随手扔了几张照片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来供我学习</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加藤鹰老师将金手指奉献给了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“可以将人的生命延长三倍”的影视事业</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功人士则将金手指奉献给了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“可以让子孙三辈不愁吃喝”的成功之道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一只I want you的手指力透屏幕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直指每一个妄想成功之人的心智</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/16d49d0c874b460d9d1640a0f2a7ba79.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200831/7a7f16a216e444579b7c70de6d98deed.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/00fe1c6c84af45b7a9d9120a7d985b7e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抚摸下巴也是成功人士的摆拍姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不管横摸竖摸，总而言之</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">胡子的密度代表成功的厚度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">胡子的长度决定谋略的深度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200831/2cf13f9980014e508d214d2c36745471.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/1783c0602e464ffda6ad6d318d550a92.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/73f772e895e44c18a0e3407d24949666.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200831/4a11e7f844b44be78bec370cae8f2ab9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而站在镜头前的那一刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西装进阶成了一袭战袍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它被加冕于一个成功男人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记载着一段商海浮沉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们穿最靓的衣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摆最拽的姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嘴里还念念有词：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“人生没有彩排</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每一天都是现场直播”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200831/6ba080959bb7411b9fd24284239d282c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/d3e7a37b28574be58cbb7ae2e7d870f6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/扯西装襟子/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200831/e3b916e75e5f47cfb8028178859340ff.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/扯领带/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功人士轻轻摩挲的尾戒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">操纵着纳斯达克股票的涨跌</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们居高临下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以鼻孔看人的同时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远处的开曼群岛就有可能</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多注册出一家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">未来中国互联网的独角兽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200831/d4a57e22782e42deb960537ea163f785.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/我是周杰伦，我为成功代言/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/77f2b7dd9a4949da9078ef4e8ed06995.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当所有姿势九九归一之时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你才能领略成功之神</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已经不是能用几个千亿来定义的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/2216017a03e940dfa330ad2dad98e6da.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/院办斯大林激情创作/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/fbb046106e1d4d36aa40fc85526703a3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我翻阅哈佛大学教授</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">埃米·卡迪（Amy Cuddy）的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《高能量姿势》一书</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">书中指出：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">舒展四肢的肢体动作被认为是强势姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而收缩四肢的姿势被认为是弱势姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/11e0da4d86484d3ea702802675906433.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如冰岛人大张大合的维京战吼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被认为是一种强势姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而双手交叉于胸前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">则属于一种弱势姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有封闭自我，进行心理防御等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">行为心理学上的解读</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/3819ec9e0be644ee9614054c7820469e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功人士和弱势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这两个词之间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明显存在矛与盾的对立</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这宣告了行为心理学</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在成功人士拍照姿势的解读上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并无用武之地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是我又请教一位微博认证为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中国图库签约摄影师的摄影师</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">试图从专业的摄影角度解读这一姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尽管他声称</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他从未给成功人士拍过照</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>至多只给成功人士的未来夫人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拍过私房写真</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/861ffee6f4cf4028bcd8bd0c16137aa4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他认为从摄影美学的原理来看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这一姿势毫无美感可言</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唯一有价值的场合是在职场中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在职场中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个姿势能彰显自信和气场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/1881e982929b4dd1bd5c41dccfb32aac.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在日常中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手交叉更多会被我们解读为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蛮横不讲理或者傲娇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而我作为旁观者看来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手交叉于胸前的姿势</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很容易让我联想到一些成语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如袖手旁观、高高在上、指点江山等</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然，任何学术的解释</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都是无意义的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我更倾向于认为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这已经成为了一种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功人士拍照的定式模板</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就像点头yes</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摇头no一样的约定俗成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看我已经悟到了这一层</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朋友东山口百惠颇是欣慰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是奖赏我一本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">江湖上失传已久的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《成功人士拍照大全》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">供我自行修炼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/4661b6a74c034db1a22c2cf58e75b680.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这本武林秘籍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将成功人士拍照姿势的一招一式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一颦一笑刻画得入木三分，力透纸背</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上面的每一个形象既有马云的影子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又是马化腾的影子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有李彦宏的影子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/af12f99c6d90414e8f1d06ea0dab3115.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那夜我通宵达旦，不看P站</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只为认真钻研</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">歪歪斜斜的每页上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都画着“成功人士”四个字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我横竖睡不着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才从图缝里看出字来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满本都写着8个字：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>欲练此功，必先成功</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200831/e520b2ee78ca404583a316247f19e848.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要想找到这个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又宽泛又抽象问题的答案</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最好的办法是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将它聚焦到每一个普通人身上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就在成功人士吧里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我窥见了一些成功的缩影</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们有的做出了正确的选择</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开四个排气管的豪车</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">戴貔貅手串</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手交叉于胸前的姿势如影随行</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至还能准确分清</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“事半功倍”和“事倍功半”的使用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是一种成功</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200831/239f70308c0a4d7e892045bda4d63fb4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有的投资千万级大电影项目</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坐等票房分账</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200831/1f965b0819a94118872b663c679136a7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就连借钱都是一万起步</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看看我蚂蚁花呗一千五的额度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我心里想着我不配</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并流下了贫穷的泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200831/2cd3c05da6af4cbfa1253cbdaeb3e384.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我几乎将百度成功人士吧的底裤翻烂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但他们终将都还是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以金钱作为衡量成功的标杆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这让我多少觉得太过于肤浅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">钻研至天亮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肚子开始宣誓它的溃不成军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是我点了一份</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">楼下房东的隆江猪脚饭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他摇曳着腰间挂着的五栋楼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笑眯眯向我走来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">步履中散发着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顶级成功人士的气息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/12f4c10eb6a844bdbde4f18d5f98de79.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他那油腻的汗衫背心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">腰间钥匙和人字拖的奇幻组合</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丝毫不亚于穿华伦天奴，开迈巴赫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及恰到好处露出的百丽翡达</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我灵机一动说：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成功人士都应该拥有一张</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">双手交叉于胸前的照片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我给你拍一张抵猪脚饭钱吧！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200831/b1138d44c5fe4a2d84715f823b17951f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">/图源于微博@郑大宝的小朋友/</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他用粤式普通话和我说：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">层功系一种气鸡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而不是一种鸡四啦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">猪脚饭15</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">房租两千都转我微信噢！</p>
